<abstract><t>In-situ Operations, Administration, and Maintenance (IOAM) collects operational and telemetry information in packets while they traverse a path between two points in the network.  This document defines two new flags in the IOAM Trace Option headers, specifically the Loopback and Active flags.</t></abstract>
